00:38:00.110 --> 00:38:02.870
we send there is very
carefully sterilized so

00:38:02.870 --> 00:38:05.590
that if we do find
life on Mars, we

00:38:05.590 --> 00:38:08.130
know that it's indigenous,
not something that we sent up

00:38:08.130 --> 00:38:09.400
there.

00:38:09.400 --> 00:38:11.210
